version_description:
Thank you for playing Pikmin Bloom!
- Improved the date of birth input form
- If you are having an issue with “This is an adult account” error message, please try to reinstall the app and enter the correct date of birth.
- Fixed a login issue with Supervised Nintendo Accounts
- Fixed an issue where a login error message was not correctly displayed
- Improved the message when location permission is not granted
